<i>But if it was,
why the hell weren't we using DHL?</i>

15:15.560 --> 15:18.882
<i>It did cross my mind to call him
and tell him I'd changed my mind.</i>

15:19.040 --> 15:21.725
<i>But the prospect of more job interviews
and queuing up at the dole office</i>

15:21.880 --> 15:23.564
<i>resolved me to stick it out.</i>

15:23.720 --> 15:26.849
<i>After all, money's money.</i>

15:54.680 --> 15:57.411
