17:11.280 --> 17:13.281
Speaking of which,
you've been doing good at the job.

17:13.440 --> 17:16.046
- It's a piece of piss.
- I know, but you never ask questions.

17:16.200 --> 17:19.602
Well, you pay me to drive, deliver shit.
