and thank you for the new games console.

19:31.920 --> 19:34.082
That's OK, mate. I didn't pay for it.
Come on.

19:34.920 --> 19:37.082
It always amazes me
that they spend all day on a computer

19:37.240 --> 19:40.210
and then in the evening wanna relax
by playing another computer game.

19:43.160 --> 19:45.083
